syntax
======

# line break - inserts a a new line
<br>

# whitespace, to get a tab repeat this 8 times (lol)
&nbsp;

# bold text
<b>this is bold text</b>

# centered text
<center>This text will be center-aligned.</center>

# a link
<a href="https://wikipedia.com">wikipedia link</a>

# a paragraph, can be replaced by two line breaks
<p>This is some text in a paragraph.</p>

# an unordered list
<ul>
	<li>coffee</li>
	<li>tea</li>
	<li>milk</li>
</ul>

# preformatted text, with all whitespaces preserved
<pre>
	- this tab is going to be visible.
&#09; - this one too (tab in hex ascii is 0x09).
</pre>

# a thematic break to separate content with a line
<hr>

